        {"data": {"id": " insolvency to inform Director of Bank Supervision   46   49B. Order vesting banking business of any licensed bank     46  49C. Order to be made after the acquiring bank agrees  to comply with terms and conditions         47  49D. Effect of an Order              47   49E. The extent of the liability of the acquiring bank in respect  of foreign currency depositors           48  49F. Audit of accounts and valuations of vested business      48  49G. Saving provisions              49   49H. Payment of compensation            49   49J. Offences                 50 ", "label": "Chunk"}},
        {"data": {"id": " Offences                 50   49K. Section 12(c) not to apply in respect of defaulting bank    50   49L. Interpretation                50   50. Liquidator                 50   51. Liquidation                50     52. Licensed commercial bank to cease to carry on business    51   53. Notice of liquidation to be sent to depositors, creditors & etc.   51   54. Safeguard rights of depositors and creditors        51   55. Licensed commercial bank removed from list of   licensed commercial banks            51", "label": "Chunk"}},
        {"data": {"id": "4 56. Compulsory liquidation             52   57. Director to take charge of all books, records and assets     52   58. Director of Bank Supervision to have full management        and control for the purpose-of liquidation        52   59. Claims &c., to be extended where liquidation proceedings   have been instituted              53         60. Power of Director of Bank Supervision to terminate contracts   53    61. Termination of fiduciary functions          53   62. Director of Bank Supervision to issue statement to depositors   53  63. Safe deposit boxes              54   64. Functions", "label": "Chunk"}},
        {"data": {"id": " boxes              54   64. Functions of Director of Bank Supervision in   relation to liquidation proceedings of a licensed commercial bank  54  65. Objection to Schedule              54   66. Priority of claims               55   67. Distribution of assets              55   68. Unclaimed funds               55   69. Audited account to be submitted to Court        56   70. Closure of licensed commercial banks incorporated outside Sri Lanka 56  71. This Part to prevail over any other law          57   72. Abandoned Property          ", "label": "Chunk"}},
