        {"data": {"id": "   60   76E. Register of specialised banks            60   76F. Cancellation of licence             60   76G. Capital to be maintained by a licensed specialised bank    60   76H. Part V and VI of this Act to apply          62   76J. Directions of the Monetary Board          62   76K. Procedure where Director of Bank Supervision is of opinion  that a licensed specialised bank is following unsound practices  65  76L. Power of Director of Bank Supervision to examine books  and accounts of a licensed specialised bank        65  76M. Winding-up or dissolution            67   76N. Power of", "label": "Chunk"}},
        {"data": {"id": " dissolution            67   76N. Power of Director of Bank Supervision to issue   directions in respect of connected matters        71  77. Declaration of secrecy              71   78. Protection for action taken under this Act or on the   directions of the Monetary Board          72  79. Offences                 72   79A. Compounding of offences            73  80. Persons who fail to take reasonable steps &c., under   the Act to be guilty of an offence          73  81. Offence by a body corporate            74   81A. Schedules II", "label": "Chunk"}},
